ISLAMABAD, Jul 26 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Monday that PML-N Secretary General Ahsan Iqbal has issued notice to a political orphan of his party, Ismael Gujjar, on his statement seeking help from India which was a good thing.
However, the minister said it would have been even better if the PML-N Central Executive Committee had issued a notice to Nawaz Sharif to probe his meeting with an enemy of Pakistan, Hamdullah Mohib, supported by India.
